videos.headline: Thompson finds Schoen wide open for 68-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson lets the ball fly 68 yards to an undefended Dalton Schoen for a Wildcats touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thompson finds Schoen wide open for 68-yard TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Campbell scores again for the Mountaineers
videos.description: Jarret Doege finds George Campbell on a scoring strike for the second time in the first quarter, this time for a 15-yard West Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Campbell scores again for the Mountaineers) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doege and Campbell connect for a 19-yard TD
videos.description: West Virginia's George Campbell gets a 19-yard lobbed touchdown pass from Jarrett Doege, putting the Mountaineers on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Doege and Campbell connect for a 19-yard TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gilbert walks into the end zone
videos.description: Kansas State's James Gilbert shuffles and finds the open gap to rush for a three-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gilbert walks into the end zone) 2019/11/16 ESHEET
